I've made this soup several times but modified it to be a non-dairy recipe. While the soup is simmering add 1/4 cup white rice. When the rice is soft, you can puree the soup and the rice becomes a great non-fat thickener (substituting for the cream). A little extra salt substitutes for the Parmesean cheese. Everyone loves it and can't believe it's all garlic and onions!

