The garlic was perfect and not overpowering. I agree, peeling all the roasted garlic was a pain - but I did it the night before and it made the actual prep. of the soup go a lot faster. I took a reviewer's advise and added bite size pieces of steamed asparagus. I highly recommend this - it was not only colorful - it really gave a unique taste. We ate this soup for 3 days!

